Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:10.73,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is there something you didn't tell me regarding
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.73,0:00:12.74,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,this meeting we're having in front of the train station?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.06,0:00:14.61,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:16.45,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I know, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.32,0:00:20.74,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I keep imagining different things!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:23.06,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Quit thinking about weird stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:24.26,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:26.28,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:26.84,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,G–{\alpha&HFF&}Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.84,0:00:27.84,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,G–Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:29.88,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,So, where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:32.88,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I'll treat you to anything you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.61,0:00:35.81,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,We're celebrating the decision of you running in the magazine. {Too long}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:36.92,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:10.09,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.09,0:02:11.74,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,when newcomers get their first run in a magazine,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:14.61,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,it has become tradition for the editorial department to treat them to a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.21,0:02:18.82,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I was saving that meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:21.08,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,You've have five more than me! {I honestly can't for the life of me hear this. Ask someone else.} {Shuujin no hoga goki okuteru}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.08,0:02:24.00,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Well I'm the one who suggested we go for yakiniku in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:26.83,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, we can just order more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:28.51,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.51,0:02:29.32,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:29.92,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Th–{\alpha&HFF&}Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:30.54,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Th–Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:33.59,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Even the ones that say "extra-special" on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:34.88,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Show some restraint.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:38.55,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,For such a joyous occasion,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:40.14,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,I would like you to have a feast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:41.26,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:45.06,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't just do nothing but celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:47.43,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're going to win against Niizuma-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.01,0:02:50.13,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as you're done eating,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:51.44,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,let's head back to the company and form our battle plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:55.44,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.47,0:02:59.69,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,In the next issue of NEXT!, there are eleven works running.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:00.49,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,One gag manga,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:02.47,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,one soccer manga,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:05.49,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,and the rest are so-called Jack-like battle mangas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:09.11,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Besides our {\i1}Kono Yo wa Kane to Chie{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.11,0:03:11.92,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,In a way, this much is just as I had calculated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:15.56,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely, Niizuma-kun will take the lead in regards to the battle mangas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:18.05,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking optimistically,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:20.37,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,it will be a one-on-one fight with Niizuma-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:21.66,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:23.93,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now for the final check on the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:24.89,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start from the first panel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.67,0:03:28.57,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,It has to be a story from beginning to end in 45 pages,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:30.48,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,so there's no way around starting with narration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:32.62,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,But you've packed too much in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:34.23,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Try to trim down the word count as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:34.86,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:37.03,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,For this computer drawing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:39.40,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,something with a more "computerish feeling" would be better, even if it seems old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:42.26,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Something that will convey a clear image to the readers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:44.24,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll do something more mechanical-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:46.20,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, second panel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:47.77,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,On the explanation of the world's structure,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.77,0:03:50.72,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,make the sentences more concise and more god-like sounding. {Someone check this. Honestly I can't figure this out.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:52.12,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:55.58,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going to go through each panel of all 45 pages, one at a time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:58.05,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but would that be a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:01.10,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:03.34,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Doing every panel like this for us is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.10,0:04:05.38,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:08.06,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Even I seriously want to win against Niizuma Eiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:09.57,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:12.20,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma-san is getting ready for serialization...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:13.42,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,so if we won against him,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:15.10,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,serialization wouldn't be just a dream anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:19.11,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you do win,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:20.99,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,I think you shouldn't be serialized for another three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:25.10,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Not until you've graduated high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:27.07,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Another three years...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:29.38,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:32.95,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,You should hone your skills and do something you're sure about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:34.53,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, third panel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:36.04,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:38.96,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,If we win against Niizuma-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:40.87,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,If we get first place in NEXT!...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:43.50,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Please think about us moving toward serialization.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:45.80,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we're aiming for with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:49.31,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about it a while now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:51.18,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,why are you in such a hurry to be serialized?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:56.98,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,I think that even Niizuma-kun is going too fast for his own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:05:00.66,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,The editorial department just wants to market him as a genius high schooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:01.94,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:04.81,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:07.17,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,We'll talk about serialization when you've beaten Niizuma-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:09.37,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,and get good results on the questionnaires.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:11.90,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:14.33,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's get back to the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:15.38,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:18.34,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro-kun, the success of this manga
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:20.88,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,will depend on well you bring out the character's expressions and mentality in your drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:25.11,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really all right with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:28.25,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,There are still trains running, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:28.84,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:31.56,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,The fare for going to Yakusa will be pretty steep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:35.70,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:37.27,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,It's just because our meeting ran late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:39.67,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,You two must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:41.16,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:44.51,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I learned plenty from all your intricate advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:46.11,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:57.02,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I want to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:06:00.54,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Especially for Hattori who did all that for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:03.64,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,A high-class meal and a serious meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:05.38,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Going home in a taxi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:10.34,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like... we're not middle schoolers anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.98,0:06:15.60,Main,Kimu,0000,0000,0000,,You sure ran late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:17.42,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:20.52,Main,Kimu,0000,0000,0000,,For only being in middle school, they sure work hard, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:23.62,Main,Kimu,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.62,0:06:27.44,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, but for some reason those two are in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:31.93,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Even about not getting serialized for three more years when they've graduated high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:34.35,Main,Kimu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:38.32,Main,Kimu,0000,0000,0000,,thee years for us is totally different from three years for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:43.82,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,You might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.98,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why KOOGY?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:51.26,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the second stage of his production plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:52.99,Up of Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:54.55,Up of Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Besides that, he's designing clothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.55,0:06:56.74,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? These are actually pretty tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:06:57.85,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Want some, Miho?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:00.95,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:04.14,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You seem down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:06.73,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, something happened with Mashiro, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:08.95,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful with those emails.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:10.70,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Misunderstandings happen.{I can't hear this line. "微妙な---" can't hear the rest.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:11.91,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,It could cause a fight.{Can't hear this either. "喧嘩の--"}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:15.03,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't exchanged emails with Mashiro yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:16.05,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:17.87,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,You told him your email address, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:20.37,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:24.00,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell how hard it is to be a mangaka just by looking at those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:26.26,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Miho...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:29.29,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you send him one, instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:31.05,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Something like, "Do your best!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.02,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Or, "I'm cheering for you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:37.95,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't... been told his email address.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:40.69,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,What's Mashiro doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:42.60,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,There are limits even to being busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:46.11,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Miho, even with us graduating so soon, are you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:49.06,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to see each other like this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:49.86,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you be lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.28,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be lying if I said I won't be lonely, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:59.47,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,Right now I want to concentrate on both of our dreams coming true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:02.43,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro-kun is working hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.43,0:08:04.25,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,so I need to work hard, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:07.97,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for caring about all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:09.32,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:11.47,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,We've been best friends since elementary school!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:14.43,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff like that's a given.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:17.42,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,We may be going to different places in high school, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:19.19,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,we'll always be together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:22.39,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:25.10,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:29.83,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,What did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:33.27,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:36.33,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy. It was decided that we're appearing in Jack NEXT!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:38.12,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're running in Jack? That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:39.37,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that make you a pro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:41.18,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's Jack NEXT!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:45.87,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,And pros are people who can make a their whole living off drawing manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:49.09,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi's so cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:51.89,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go telling Azuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:53.27,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:54.97,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:57.86,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.86,0:09:00.22,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Miho told me not to tell you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.78,0:09:02.83,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,That sort of thing happens a lot with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:04.56,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,If someone tells you not to say something, don't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:06.27,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Miho's moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:07.55,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:08.11,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:09.98,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,To Hachiouji.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:12.24,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be that she...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:14.53,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Because of how they're not meeting until their dreams come true...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:16.11,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:18.74,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell Mashiro, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.09,0:09:24.29,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,If Azuki said not to, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:26.90,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Is she going to tell him herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:29.21,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a little before she moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:30.66,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Then... {This one wasn't translated. I'm not sure if it means "Then..." or something else. Needs TLC.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:32.95,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,But don't you think they'll be lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:36.29,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,That will make it easier for both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:39.86,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:44.35,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,before Miho moves and before they graduate,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.68,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,get Miho and Mashiro have one date!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:48.15,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,They should do at least that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:51.71,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they won't kiss, they can at least hold hands and wish each other luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:54.28,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Those two... If they are alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:56.99,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think they would even speak to each other, let alone hold hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:58.85,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Even that is good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:00.37,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they just look each other in the eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:03.79,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,But if you try to make Saikou and her do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:05.45,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,they probably won't be happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:07.91,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:10.38,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,If Mashiro invited her, Miho would definitely be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:13.60,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,But they promised not to see each other until their dreams came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:16.97,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she would be happy if she was told he wanted to date her once before graduation. {Re-word}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.89,0:10:20.59,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of person she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:23.06,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:27.48,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Are those two... just going to keep this up and say goodbye at graduation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:29.44,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Until their dreams come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:31.13,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,When will that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:32.65,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Is it certain that they will come true someday?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:42.87,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I–If they really like each other, then they wouldn't need their dreams to come true, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:45.49,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:53.21,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:54.92,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:56.42,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It might be a waste of time, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:57.76,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:10:59.09,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,You were faking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:00.81,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm different. {Uhh...}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:06.93,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki's moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:09.52,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:16.12,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,So... we thought it might be nice if the two of you could talk one time before she moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.54,0:11:20.50,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,We need to win against Eiji and get first place in the questionnaires.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:23.03,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have that kind of spare time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:24.78,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.21,0:11:29.41,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why didn't Azuki tell me herself?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:31.87,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,But just a little chat wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.03,0:11:33.75,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,We won't meet until after our dreams have come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:35.38,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Not before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.68,Main,Miyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you being so stubborn?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:38.87,Main,Miyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you some kind of idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:40.05,Main,Miyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,You just won't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:40.64,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Miyoshi, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:43.14,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand girls' feelings at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:44.47,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I feel bad for Miho.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:47.68,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I understand Azuki better than you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:49.23,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,You do not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:50.82,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a clue!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.82,0:11:52.64,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way she wouldn't be happy to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:53.43,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.43,0:11:56.98,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Cool down a minute, Miyoshi. Saikou, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:55.20,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,This is a promise we made between the two of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:57.60,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you promise something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:11:59.53,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Some outsider like you shouldn't be butting in like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:11.00,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that wasn't going to go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:14.56,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Saikou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:15.81,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,How about we leave for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:18.50,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the the part of the name I fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:21.20,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Miyoshi doesn't mean anything bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:22.30,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Please understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:25.13,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,You know, that's just how she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.13,0:12:26.43,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,She gets a little wild sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:28.03,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I known.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:30.97,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'd better follow after Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:32.01,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Saikou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:32.73,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:38.81,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Azuki's moving.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:41.89,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's not like she's leaving the country or anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:44.01,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And until our dreams come true,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:45.69,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}no matter where she is, it will be the same.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:49.31,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we both work hard,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:51.40,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}those dreams will come true sooner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:53.11,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until then, just like Uncle,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:55.60,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll just look at our graduation album.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:57.67,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll encourage each other just through email.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:04.51,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:07.14,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When are we going to get serialized?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:19.85,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:20.94,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou, you're early.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:23.14,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,So are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:25.65,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my parents forgot to turn on the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:28.05,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,There is heating here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:30.50,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold out, so I took refuge here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:31.76,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Heaters sure are nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:32.95,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Wish I had one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:36.21,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if someone would buy what's inside my head for around 100 million?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:40.63,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,How much do yakiniku do you think you could eat if you had 100 million?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:43.14,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I ate all that before,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:45.04,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,You're the real glutton. {Can't hear} {Hounto koija hatena} { ┐(￣ー￣)┌ }
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.04,0:13:47.94,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It was like you had two bodies, Saikou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:49.14,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Sure was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:53.62,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Shuujin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.62,0:13:54.99,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:56.71,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,You were watching out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.22,0:14:00.94,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I must apologize to Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:03.93,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I called her an outsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:07.51,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,She might not forgive me after so long, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:08.89,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if I make a call?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:10.07,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? To whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:12.20,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:14.66,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.15,0:14:16.12,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:18.22,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,After thinking about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:22.84,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I realized this is a matter about how you two feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:27.35,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my cool and couldn't restrain myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.35,0:14:28.63,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Then I said some things I shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:32.02,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,So I take back what I said yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:33.50,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:34.14,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:35.50,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:37.70,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I said some mean things when I got angry, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:39.47,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,so we're in the same boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:40.35,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:44.32,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, thanks for worrying about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:48.12,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, now it's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:51.20,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of feel like we dragged you into all of this, Shuujin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.53,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's just your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:25.22,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:27.00,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:28.07,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:29.03,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,The name was OK'd.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:30.82,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:32.46,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,but that means you're making progress, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:33.07,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:35.04,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.04,0:15:36.92,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Now we can finally make it a manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:38.62,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you still have to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:40.65,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, now it's the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.65,0:15:44.56,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Inking, backgrounds, filling in darks, tones, effects, whiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:46.88,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Woah, there's a lot to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:49.79,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Being a mangaka is quite hard, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:50.84,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,So you finally get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:53.65,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:55.97,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of thought we could go out together,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:57.97,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,but it looks like you're busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.26,0:15:59.51,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:00.60,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:01.60,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:04.10,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to leave early today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:07.07,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,We're not starting for real stuff until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:10.86,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really leaving early?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:12.57,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:21.12,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,So is it okay if we leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:23.08,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:24.68,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:25.57,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:26.29,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:27.86,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:29.08,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.57,0:16:41.32,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,So, where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.32,0:16:43.02,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have much time, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:47.52,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Our usual park?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.62,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,You're really okay with here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:50.48,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:52.82,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:55.96,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:56.82,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:59.20,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Mashiro said all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:01.04,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,there's no way he's going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:03.95,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,They're not going to meet until their dreams come true,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.95,0:17:08.36,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,so he's doing his best with manga so he can see Azuki even one day sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:09.61,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:12.26,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're starting to understand Saikou a little bit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:17.38,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,So then, Mashiro really wants to see Miho a lot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:18.09,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Miho does, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.02,0:17:21.63,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Those two really won't let this go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.26,0:17:24.94,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you not interfering with those two anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:26.95,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.95,0:17:28.31,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Then leave it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:30.18,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,You're poking your nose in too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:36.99,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, at school...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:40.93,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Miho and Mashiro have been acting awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:43.12,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,It's like they're avoiding each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:47.01,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,They may be together until graduation, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:51.04,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,are they really all right with these being their memories of the end of middle school?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:54.09,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:18:00.48,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,You really are poking your nose in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:01.47,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:04.43,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of like that about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:10.85,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Say that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:13.08,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,My heart wasn't ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:14.80,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I–{\alpha&HFF&}I kind of don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:15.49,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I–I kind of don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:17.55,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:18.63,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.63,0:18:19.45,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.81,0:18:21.15,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,You cheapskate, Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:22.47,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with being a cheapskate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:24.91,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I just thought of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:25.58,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:28.92,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,A way to make memories for Azuki and Saikou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:36.30,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I think we must say that we, juniors, have been taught a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:40.84,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to leave you saying that we've benefited from their by having the upperclassmen at this school,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:46.27,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,and we pray that you have prepared well for your future. {can't hear}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:53.10,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Now for the graduating class response address.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:54.35,Main,Iwase,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:05.87,Main,Iwase,0000,0000,0000,,Reply address, by graduate representative Iwase Aiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.63,0:19:08.83,Main,Suzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your spirits up, Saikou!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:12.08,Main,Suzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to different high schools, but I'll always be cheering you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:13.09,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,O–{\alpha&HFF&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:13.92,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,O–Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:14.88,Main,Suzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:15.40,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,R–{\alpha&HFF&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:16.08,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,R–Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:17.23,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:18.80,Main,Suzuki,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:19.92,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Your snot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:21.87,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:23.05,Main,Ishizawa,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:25.41,Main,Mashiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ishizawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.23,0:19:28.64,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Ishizawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.05,0:19:33.33,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive you, but I'm was wrong to hit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:34.76,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:37.23,Main,Ishizawa,0000,0000,0000,,Give it your all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:42.65,Main,Suzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What did that guy come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:43.78,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time we go, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:45.29,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.18,0:19:47.92,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hang out again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:48.58,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:53.75,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you about how I got a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:55.91,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,Kaya, it's about time we head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:56.46,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.69,0:19:57.84,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Miho...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:00.17,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with Miho?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:01.91,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'll email you again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:02.93,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:10.44,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Shuujin...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:11.06,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:14.73,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki already went home...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.14,0:20:21.95,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Miyoshi said she was going to take her time walking home with Azuki on graduation day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.31,0:20:25.28,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.74,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered something I have to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:28.85,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.84,0:20:33.87,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Miho, look! There's a weed growing in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:35.65,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Life sure is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:38.25,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,Kaya, you sure like weeds today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.79,0:20:38.91,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I–{\alpha&HFF&}I–Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.91,0:20:39.21,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I–I–{\alpha&HFF&}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:40.18,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I–I–Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.18,0:20:41.84,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,This is the third time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.94,0:20:46.09,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Man, she's home already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:49.72,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Miho, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.41,0:21:01.26,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be taking my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:01.65,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,See ya later!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:03.99,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:22.63,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Miho, you idiot, don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.91,0:21:25.51,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro obviously came here for a reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.66,0:21:27.22,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:29.18,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Fight, Saikou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:32.71,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must say something...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:36.85,Main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Bad girl, Merry-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:47.66,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must say something soon...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.54,0:21:51.08,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But what should it be...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.60,0:21:54.41,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Um...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.89,0:21:56.87,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,How long...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.11,0:21:59.83,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,How long will you wait for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.83,0:22:07.88,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.98,0:22:25.72,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}I'll wait forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.81,0:22:37.66,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it with just "I'll wait."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.86,0:22:40.19,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,March 21,{\alpha&HFF&} 2009.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.19,0:22:41.29,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,March 21, 2009.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.01,0:22:45.09,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,We graduated middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Ending}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.75,0:24:18.34,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki's waiting for me. What I need to do now is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.34,0:24:20.40,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Finish "Kono Yo wa Kane to Chie", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.40,0:24:22.21,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't want to lose to Eiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.21,0:24:22.60,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.13,0:24:23.74,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Next time,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.74,0:24:25.14,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Early Report and Real Deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.14,0:24:27.93,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Jack NEXT! is the first step towards our dream!
